            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://www.vox.com/2014/5/20/5732208/the-green-lantern-theory-of-the-presidency-explained",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " mocking those who suggested that the most powerful man on Earth has any power to influence elected officials in his own party. Obama is still ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "pretending",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
